description: It gets more interesting by the day. 🍿✌️🌈❤️ is this what Australian’s standing together looks like? I am deeply concerned and disappointed and find this absolutely appalling.  Even if this is their attempt at humour, do you find it funny at this time in human history when censoring of freedom of speech is happening?  My message to all Australians is use your voice if you feel called to #unitedwestand #idonotconsent
